{"tid":578843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"考DSE 最多可以報考幾多科？想挑戰自己","createTime":"2018-03-03T04:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T05:09:03.000Z","uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7efa6e30110ea7ff35ccdcd6ab80f44d6bb9b169","tid":578843,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:37:21.000Z","msg":"甲類科目- 24科高中科目<br />\n乙類科目- 36科應用學習科<br />\n<br />\n最多可以報考幾多科？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ce6db43d10dc08612cbfb17793b1c4e894b5f1","tid":578843,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:38:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"992ff5284ca51c0520d5c62e17e8308ad4701437","tid":578843,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:43:24.000Z","msg":"原來考生最多可報考八科。所報考之科目可從甲、乙及丙三個學科類別中 挑選。若考生選擇報考數學科的延伸部分，則該部分的成績將與必修 部分的成績分別列出，然而延伸部分並不視爲額外的一個科目。此 外，若考生選擇報考八科，則至少其中一科必須屬下列範疇的科目:<br />\n(a) 甲類學科中的倫理與宗教/音樂/體育/視覺藝術 (b) 乙類學科中的應用學習科目<br />\n(c) 丙類學科中的其他語言科目"},{"pid":"8a2a3286c5c93652cb49731580e6e08e7d775455","tid":578843,"uid":96435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:43:49.000Z","msg":"九科包m1/m2<br />\n4C+4X<br />\n其中一科X要係音樂或者Art<br />\n另外冇喺日校讀過phy chem bio唔報得呢三科<br />\nAL巴打係時候入去做鳩19DSE雞了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b2f05965770cd60889193fdecb91f70be03a84","tid":578843,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a2a3286c5c93652cb49731580e6e08e7d775455","tid":578843,"uid":96435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:43:49.000Z","msg":"九科包m1/m2<br />\n4C+4X<br />\n其中一科X要係音樂或者Art<br />\n另外冇喺日校讀過phy chem bio唔報得呢三科<br />\nAL巴打係時候入去做鳩19DSE雞了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:46:56.000Z","msg":"AL 巴打係時候去考吓中英文 oral listening<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得帶部接收強勁既收音機，或者有咩事就舉手去特別室，分分鐘坐爆間房"},{"pid":"7e9c2315a4309a10d38e9aac3c887ffb56ef2150","tid":578843,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:50:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49e8f92f484600c5e77f8ed50f316d3e7b1c854b","tid":578843,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e9c2315a4309a10d38e9aac3c887ffb56ef2150","tid":578843,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:50:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:54:38.000Z","msg":"哎吔哋 政府又要洗錢了"},{"pid":"d3b41f0176cb8f8fac121e99fe81fa46792cdfb7","tid":578843,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:09:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}